<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1"?>
<aiml>


    
    <category>
        <pattern>NOANSWER</pattern>
        <template>
            I'm not one of the three master djinns, so I can't answer you...
        </template>
    </category>   

   

    <category>
        <pattern>RESPONSEABOUTALPHAORB</pattern>
        <template>
            <srai>GETBOTNAME</srai>
            <condition name="botName">
                <li value="Pay Rhuss">
                    A father and his future son-in-law sharing the same meal tonight. He who indulges
                        in uncovering the secrets of earthly light and matter, is unintentionnaly
                        attempting to do the same with Heavenly Ones.
                </li>
                <li value="Phayl Blogg">
                    Where does the squirrel hide his bounty ? He will never say. But his investigating
                        maiden might; too bad she's so far north from here.
                </li>
                <li value="Sheuk Nauriss">
                    The man would die rather than revealing where his precious is. But the woman
                        would be sensible enough to prefer her life to a shiny stone.
                </li>
                <li>
                 <srai>NOANSWER</srai>               
                </li>
            </condition>
        </template>
    </category>


    <category>
        <pattern>RESPONSEABOUTBETAORB</pattern>
        <template>
            <srai>GETBOTNAME</srai>
            <condition name="botName">
                <li value="Pay Rhuss">
                    Long times ago, heathens have found, in an underground temple, a marvellous
                        stone. Lucky them, it was nothing less than a Divine Tear.
                </li>
                <li value="Phayl Blogg">
                    How may one imagine greater sacrilege, than having a Heart of Purity jailed,
                        for one decade already, in one of the darkest citadels of our western
                        neighbours?
                </li>
                <li value="Sheuk Nauriss">
                    I guess masslavian agents know better than me where their orb is imprisoned.
                        Don't your fellows have the power to question them?
                </li>
                <li>
                 <srai>NOANSWER</srai>               
                </li>
            </condition>
        </template>
    </category>

    <category>
        <pattern>RESPONSEABOUTGAMMAORB</pattern>
        <template>
            <srai>GETBOTNAME</srai>
            <condition name="botName">
                <li value="Pay Rhuss">
                    In the past, courageous zealots have tried to save their last treasure from
                        the hands of miscreants. They have been so successful, that to this
                        day no one has ever seen it again.
                </li>
                <li value="Phayl Blogg">
                    Only the seeker of the past, the awakener of forsaken tongues, might eventually
                        uncover the Divine Pearl burrowed in an endlessly frozen land.
                </li>
                <li value="Sheuk Nauriss">
                    Salt is like water or sun : too little and there is no life, too much and
                        there is no life either. And there used to be too much in southern countries.
                        The statue of Bartzar would confirm my assertions.
                </li>
                <li>
                 <srai>NOANSWER</srai>               
                </li>
            </condition>
        </template>
    </category>

   
    <category>
        <pattern>RESPONSEABOUTOTHERORBS</pattern>
        <template>
            <srai>GETBOTNAME</srai>
            <condition name="botName">
                <li value="Pay Rhuss">
                    Not one, not two, but three Celestial Tears, have invited themselves to the
                    mundane gathering, via the foolish carelessness of brilliant minds,
                    the mysterious testimony of ancestral signs, and the worried soul of
                    heathens.
                </li>
                <li value="Phayl Blogg">
                    Sheuk Nauriss knows so much more than me... But I can help anyway.
                </li>
                <li value="Sheuk Nauriss">
                    Time is running out. So many people are seeking these famous Orbs...
                </li>
                <li>
                 <srai>NOANSWER</srai>               
                </li>
            </condition>
        </template>
    </category>
    
   
    <category>
        <pattern>RESPONSEABOUTCYNTHIA</pattern>
        <template>
            <srai>GETBOTNAME</srai>
            <condition name="botName">
                <li value="Pay Rhuss">
                    Who knows... Irony, the young reporter might actually reveal herself much more important
                        than the Nalavut leaders she sought to interview.
                </li>
                <li value="Phayl Blogg">
                    The struggle for power is surrounding the wife of the physicist. He who holds
                        her, will also hold a Divine Tear.
                </li>
                <li value="Sheuk Nauriss">
                    It seems your fellows plan to seek refuge near this peaceful place called
                        Aklarvik
                </li>
            </condition>
        </template>
    </category>
</aiml>